---
import SectionLabel from './ui/SectionLabel.astro';
---

<section class="bg-sand py-section animate-on-scroll">
  <div class="max-w-narrow mx-auto px-6">

    <SectionLabel text="The Outcome" />

    <h2 class="font-serif text-heading-mobile md:text-heading text-charcoal mb-8">
      What changes when execution becomes measurable.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-5 font-sans text-lg text-warm-gray leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        You end every Friday knowing exactly what you executed and what you didn't. Not a feeling — a number.
        Your execution score is right there: 87%.
      </p>
      <p>
        Your manager notices. Deadlines hit. Projects move. That strategic initiative you've been
        'planning to start' for six months? It's in week 8. On track.
      </p>
      <p>
        The compounding effect is the real prize. One consistent quarter changes how people see you.
        Two consistent quarters changes your career trajectory.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
